<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Thomas" baseAuthorityYear="1911" box="[344,472,2227,2260]" class="Mammalia" family="Talpidae" genus="Uropsilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="3" pageNumber="598" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="gracilis">U. gracilis</taxonomicName>
, which is classified as Least Concern.
</paragraph>
